# FreeYFi Frontend Rules

## Before coding
Read `y_fi_frontend/.cursor/workflow/README.md`.

## After coding
Append to `.cursor/workflow/changelog.md` with `YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM (UTC+6)`. Update `api-integration.md` if API usage changes. Automatic — see `auto-changelog.mdc`.

## Stack
React 18 + Vite 6 + Tailwind 4 + React Router 7. JavaScript only (no TS).

## API calls
Use `API_BASE` from `src/lib/api.js` for all backend requests. Do not hardcode production URLs.

## Pages
- `src/app/pages/` — Home, Contact, Privacy
- `src/routes.js` — route table
- `src/app/mainoutlate.jsx` — layout shell

## Deploy
CI serves committed `dist/`. Run `yarn build` before deploy if UI changed.

## Multi-model review
Use for contact form API changes, APK download flow, or privacy policy updates.
